caption: I’ve been to this place 4 or 5 times now. Every time I have to wait 30+ minutes for my food even though the food is premade and is just sitting out there. Literally all they need to do is scooping the food into the container. And honestly the food isn’t that good. The chicken is so dry. And the pork is so hard to chew. I wouldn’t even go here a second time if it’s not so close to me.  Today I decided to give it another try. The cashier got my order wrong. I told her and she just brushed me off and started talking to the next customer.  I’m never going back again.

The staff in this restaurant is so RUDE & Unprofessional!! 1st of all I ordered three plates of griot fritay for 44$ and in the plate I only received griot and plantains where was the rest of the food? what got to me was they had the nerve to get mad when my mother confronted them about it, but when we got home to eat the food and it was not good at all!  Im just disappointed with Kreyol Flavor! (THUMBS DOWN)
